@startuml Project Status State Diagram
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam roundcorner 10

title Project Status State Machine

state "Planning" as Planning
state "Active" as Active
state "On Hold" as OnHold
state "Completed" as Completed
state "Cancelled" as Cancelled

[*] --> Planning : Project created

Planning --> Active : Start project
Active --> OnHold : Pause project
OnHold --> Active : Resume project
Active --> Completed : Complete project
Active --> Cancelled : Cancel project
OnHold --> Cancelled : Cancel project
Planning --> Cancelled : Cancel project

Completed --> [*] : Project finished
Cancelled --> [*] : Project removed

note right of Planning
  **Initial State:**
  - Project created
  - Planning phase
  - Can assign team
end note

note right of Active
  **Active State:**
  - Project in execution
  - Tasks being worked on
  - Can be paused
end note

note right of OnHold
  **Paused State:**
  - Project temporarily stopped
  - Can be resumed
  - Can be cancelled
end note

note right of Completed
  **Final State:**
  - Project finished
  - end_date set
  - All tasks completed
end note

note right of Cancelled
  **Final State:**
  - Project cancelled
  - Cannot be resumed
  - end_date set
end note

@enduml

